dungeon.datastructures

Class ListNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • dungeon.datastructures.ListNode

  • public class ListNode
extends Object
    A limited linked list that's used by the IndexOfLists structure. It stores Coordinates objects as value, and points to the following ListNode to create the list. It supports getValue(), listContains(), addValue(), removeValue(), with a host of private and help methods.
    Author:
    tgtapio

      • addValue

        public boolean addValue(int key,
                        CoordinatesList value)
        Finds and replaces the first deleted node with given information. If no deleted node is found, a new one is generated at the end of the list.
        Parameters:
        key - of the value
        value - is a list of coordinates
        Returns:
